Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我研究了薩道克那本舊書\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was sifting through Sadoc's old book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,毛腳族很久以前就走過這條路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harfoots must've journeyed this way a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯塔爾一定會屈服在我手下 不然的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Istar will surrender to me, because if he doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我就殺了他稱之爲朋友的半身人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will slaughter the halflings he calls friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要往山脊線去嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were you headed for the ridgeline?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,倖存者會在紮營處等我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The survivors will be waiting for us where we made camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,–還有我父親 –你可能錯過他們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My father, too. - I think you may have missed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,–你也在找家人嗎  –我未婚夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hoping to find kin as well? My betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他有你一半堅強 我敢肯定他會撐過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he's even half as strong as you, I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒你想的那麼堅強\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not so strong as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之間曾有的關聯 現在也化爲灰燼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you were to me, is ashes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是覺得 我們沒必要再交談了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So for my part, we don't ever need to speak again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你真想找回你的馬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D'you really want your horse back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,–你知道它在哪  –今晚這裏見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know where he is? - Meet me here. Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼 你那麼晚在外面幹嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doin' out here in the dark, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有埋伏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,領主大人 準備工作就快完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Preparations are nearly complete, Lord-father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要再次開戰嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must we go to war again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,除非確定索隆徹底消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll never truly be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們永遠不會真正安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until we've made certain Sauron is no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,自從戴上這枚戒指 我能感知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since the wearing of this Ring, I have perceived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不可見世界的閃現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}glimpses of the unseen world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們送去給凱勒布林博的消息 都沒有迴音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our letters to Celebrimbor have all gone unanswered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我擔心索隆已經潛入埃瑞吉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fear Sauron may be in Eregion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,至高王同意我帶一小隊人馬過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The High King has consented to send me and a small party there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,確定凱勒布林博和埃瑞吉安很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to ensure Celebrimbor and his city are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,埃爾隆德的任務不是加入你的陣容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond's task is not to join your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而是領導陣容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But to lead it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}指環王:力量之戒\N第二季第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs21}本WEB版外掛字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}風吹來的那片雲{\c&HFFFFFF&}  雙語合併
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,凱勒布林博還是沒回復...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still no word from Celebrimbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果走阿克薩橋 不到730公里就能到埃瑞吉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we take the Axa Bridge, Eregion is just under 150 leagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要一名弓箭手 兩名劍士 相信你能推薦好人選\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We shall need an archer, two swordsmen. I trust you can recommend a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,相信 我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定這樣好嗎 指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you certain that's wise, commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在至高王的催促下 我同意任命你爲第二指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the High King's urging, I agreed to appointment you as first lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你認爲有失你的身份 我會另擇他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you deem that duty beneath you, I will choose another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,–是的 –什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. -"Yes" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我能推薦 一名弓箭手和兩名劍士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I can recommend an archer and two swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,還要帶誰去 指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else shall we take with us, commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,閃電\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有任何世俗力量能辦到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No earthly force could do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是索隆的傑作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the work of Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,坎尼爾 還有哪條路能走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Camnir. What other paths might we take?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要繞過去的話 我們要麼往北\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To circumvent it, we shall either have to turn due north,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,多花兩週時間...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}adding two weeks to our journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不然呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不然往南 穿越圖林戈沙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go south, through the Hills of Tyrn Gorthad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,到埃瑞吉安會快很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which will get us to Eregion much faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏有邪惡之物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is evil in those hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,存在久遠 充滿惡意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ancient, and filled with malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,索隆故意要我們走那條路 我們必須走另一條\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauron means for us to go that way. We must go another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大敵肯定兩條路都監視着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Enemy is doubtless watching both roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看這坍塌 我們要更快趕到凱勒布林博那兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This collapse makes it more critical than ever to reach Celebrimbor at speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一走進陷阱我們哪都到不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We won't reach anywhere at speed if we walk into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,往南走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,指揮官 我得反對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander, I must protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽到你的意見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your opinion on the matter has been heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到了 第二指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Opinion heard, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們往南走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不會聽從那小玩意的建議 你也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This company will not take counsel from that trinket, nor will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不能遵守這些條件 你現在就回林頓去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you cannot abide by those terms, you will leave now and return to Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,–我是很想 –那爲何不走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I should like to. - Then why do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲我不想看到有人送命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I do not wish to see any of this company slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,諾瑞 波比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori! Poppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你有看到兩個半身人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pardon me. I don't suppose you've seen a pair of halflings come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你找到羔羊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See you found the goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找的...不是羔羊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't... quite what I was searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你要找的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's what you're searchin' for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你也找到了 對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and there's what you find, now, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,歡樂咚 快活咚 敲響叮叮咚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey dol, merry dol Ring a dong dillow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,白蛉草地飛 蜜蜂柳樹轉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sandflies in the grass Bees around the willow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你的山丘上方有星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are some stars above your hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,山丘上方常有星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stars above most 'ills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我朋友在找這些星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But my friends and I were looking for these stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來希望...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had hoped that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My apologies, j-just a moment--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,歌唱那太陽 星星 月亮與輕霧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of sun, stars Moon and mist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雨水與雲天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rain and cloudy weather
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,魔杖...當然了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The branch... of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. It must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,波比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,–有看到他嗎  –誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D'you see him? - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你說咧 我們的朋友 那天殺的異鄉人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who d'you think? Our friend, the bleedin' Stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先別管他在哪 我們在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never mind where's he, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,諾瑞 快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 應該是甩掉他們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think, I think we lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你們哪來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you lot come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你又是哪來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腦袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,–我住這 –毛腳族住這\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Live here. - Harfoots live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,毛腳族是什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's an Harfoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you are--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是無名仔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能是“無名仔”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you can't be "Nobody."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都這麼叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... That's what everybody calls me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果大家都叫你無名仔 沒人叫你某某某嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If everybody calls you Nobody, doesn't anybody call you somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我媽叫我梅里麥克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, my mum calls me Merimac.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是波比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Poppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我是諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Nori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的水從哪弄來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you get that water from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,–小聲一點 –偷來的 對不對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep your voice down. You stole it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,從大傢伙那口井偷來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stole it from that well. From the big folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,–你去哪  –沒有啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But-- Where are you going? Uh, nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,帶我們一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take us with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 村子嚴禁外人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, sorry, no outsiders in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,村子 什麼村子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Village? What village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 沒有村子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No village! There's no village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,給我聽好 無名仔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen here, Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要麼讓我們跟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either we're coming with you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不然就告發你 偷水賊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or I will turn you in myself this moment, water-thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你們待會兒會見到阿古 我們的領袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're about to meet The Gund, our dwell-leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,想要她考慮收留你們 要遵守四條規定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you want her to even think about takin' you in, there's four rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,第一 不要直視她的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, never look her in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,第二 永遠距離她三步遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}B, always stand three steps back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,第四 不管怎樣 千萬不要叫她阿古\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Four, don't, ever, ever, no matter what, call her "The Gund."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,–瞭解 –瞭解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Got it. - Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,規定是三條還四條\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was that three rules or four?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒認真聽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't really paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 好好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Off you go, have fun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊 那邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因爲有陽光照射\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's 'cause it's had the sunshine on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看那裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 很新鮮 可以剝皮了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice, fresh batch, ready to peel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,–大帽子 跟我的一樣  –跟爸的一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big hat, like mine! Like Dad's!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,毛腳族住在洞穴裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harfoots, livin' in holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,–感覺怪怪的 –因爲我們不是毛腳族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It doesn't seem natural. -That's 'cause we're not Harfoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是壯軀族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're Stoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,壯軀族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stoors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事帶她們來幹嘛 沒有人那麼笨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What were you thinkin', bringin' 'em here? Nobody's that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她們需要一個藏身處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They needed a place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎樣 沙漠裏有魔鬼要抓她們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, with half the devils in the desert searchin' for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼 要是禿鷹吞了你腦袋 肯定倒退飛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boy, if we put your brains in a vulture, it'd fly backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,別對他那麼兇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be nicer to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在頂撞我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you talkin' back-sass to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是第四條規定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that was the fourth rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,給我一個好理由不把你們丟出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me one good reason why I shouldn't feed you leg, limb, and joint
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,送給那些追殺你們的高德林人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to those Gaudrim hunting you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,說啊 我聽聽看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, plead your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我淌過河流 越過高山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have walked across rivers, and mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,穿過沙漠 幫助我的朋友尋找他的天命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and deserts to help my friend find his destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他的天命可能左右着 這世界的命運 包括你們...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one the fate of the world may well depend on, yours included--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我說給我一個好理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said one good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你那個朋友 他是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This friend of yours, who is he, anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,–他是個巨人 –巨人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's a giant. - A giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,–什麼 像精靈嗎  –比精靈更大尾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What, like an Elf? - Bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他是超大隻精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So he's a great big Grand-Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他是個巫師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這片天空下唯一的巫師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the only wizard under these skies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是黑巫師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is the Dark Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們最不需要的朋友就是他的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the last friend we need is a friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把她們綁起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tie 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,放開她 黑巫師是什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Let her go. What Dark Wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯塔爾變得 比我們預期的更加強大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Istar is already much more powerful than we had anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他憑空召喚出沙塵暴 殺了我兩名手下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He conjured a sandstorm from thin air that killed two of my men,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他現在往北去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He makes his way north now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,往...那隱士的方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Towards... the hermit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那兩個半身人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what of the halflings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正在沙漠搜索 她們躲不了太久的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are scouring the desert even now. They will not evade us for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我以性命發誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear my life on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,高德林人 你要不是很笨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are either very foolish, Gaudrim,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是很勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你專心處理那兩個毛腳族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let the Harfoots be your sole concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯塔爾交給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will see to the Istar myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再放他出來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let him out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不該醒來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should not be wakin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,吃土壤 挖深點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eat earth. Dig deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喝點水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drink water, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,去睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒人叫我什麼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Been awhile since I've been called much of anythin',
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,以前在柳條河一帶 大家都叫我邦巴迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but back in the Withywindle, folk used to call me Bombadil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,湯姆邦巴迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom Bombadil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太陽西沉啦 快要摸黑啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Down west sinks the sun Soon you will be gropin'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,別害羞了 金莓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be bashful now, Goldberry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,夜影來臨時 家門爲你開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the night-shadows fall Then the door will open
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經很努力洗你的髒袍子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done such as I can with your filthy robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,洗洗手 洗洗臉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, clean your hands, wash your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,過來跟我一起烤火吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then come join me by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,外面還有其他人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is, uh... Is somebody out there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像聽到一個女人在唱歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I heard a woman singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,女人 什麼女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Woman? What woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏沒有其他人在嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is no one else here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你在啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is, I think you are. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 你本來希望 在星星下面找到什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, what was it that you were hopin' to find under those stars of yours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不會是老湯姆吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainly not old Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,希望找到我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was hoping to find my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,星星又懂什麼呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shows what stars know, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它們就是新來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Newcomers, that's what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,某一年還很暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One year, it's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,下一年 你擡頭看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next, you look up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,發現一大片小眼睛往下盯着你看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a sea of tiny eyes lookin' down at ya, a-watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它們以爲自己無所不知 但不過就是新來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, they think they know everythin', but newcomers. Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還嫩得很\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still newcomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你還不知道我名字嗎  那是唯一的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you know my name yet? That's the only answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我纔想問你是什麼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, who are you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,孤身一人 無名無姓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}alone, yourself, and nameless?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你年輕 我已經老了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you are young, and I am old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是個最老之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eldest, that's what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“最老之人”是什麼意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean, "Eldest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是最老之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,記住我的話 朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mark my words, friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在河流和樹木出現前 湯姆就在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom was there before the river and the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,湯姆記得第一滴雨滴和第一顆橡實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom remembers the first raindrop and the first acorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他看過星空之下沒有恐懼的黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knew the dark under the stars when it was fearless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏曾一片青蔥翠綠 現在全是沙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This whole place used to be green. Now, it's all sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我還得親眼目睹纔敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to come see for myself to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,連鳥鳴聲都受影響\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the birdsong isn't wholly untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,連外面那棵老鐵木也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even your tree out there. Old Man Ironwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我以爲它...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought it--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他或許願意借我一根樹枝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He... might be able to, lend me a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該問問他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well you should've tried askin' him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放輕鬆 伊爾溫 放輕鬆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy, Iarwain. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這種...魔法 你能教我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This... magic. Can you teach it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,教你 這裏有什麼好學的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Teach you? What's to learn way out 'ere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你能控制樹 控制風和火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wield power over trees, over wind and fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像它們屬於你一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wield it, as if it belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,天地萬物都屬於它們自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All things belong each to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你屬於你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as you belong to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那你能教我該怎麼使用魔杖嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, might you teach me how to wield a staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,巫師的魔杖就像名字一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A wizard's staff is like a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,本來就屬於你 你只要證明自己配得上它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's yours to wield already, if you prove yourself worthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天證明了你還不夠格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You showed today that you're not. Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能變得夠格 我們很快就會知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whether you can become so, well, we shall soon discover.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這些星星下要找的不是魔杖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was never meant to find a staff under these stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而是你 對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was meant to find you. Wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:22:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有伴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麼要追殺我和我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do they hunt me, and my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是第一個 在我火堆旁吃蜂蜜的伊斯塔爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are not the first Istar who's eaten honey by my fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很多年前有另一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Years ago, there was another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,黑巫師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Dark Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他後來怎麼樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What became of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他也曾跟你一樣想掌控魔法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once, he sought to control magic, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,現在他掌控了大部分魯恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, he controls much of Rh?n.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但仍然渴望得到更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But still, he hungers for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你擔心他的邪惡會蔓延\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You believe his evil will spread?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,除非有比他更強大的盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not without an ally far more powerful even than himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要是這兩團烈火合而爲一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If these two flames combine into one,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,中洲將無盡燃燒 直到灰飛煙滅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there will be no end to burnin', till all Middle-earth is ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.45,0:24:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你能阻止嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老湯姆是個漫遊者 不是戰士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Tom's a wanderer, not a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,偉大事蹟要交付命定之人手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great deeds are left to the hands they were placed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.75,0:24:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要趁睡蓮生長之時採摘它們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I shall gather lilies, while yet they grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.16,0:24:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.54,0:24:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,交付我手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.83,0:24:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的使命是阻止這場烈火嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it my task to stop the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.66,0:24:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的使命是面對索隆嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it my task to face Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.91,0:25:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的使命 是面對他們倆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your task... is to face them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.50,0:25:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我等着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.54,0:25:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,圖林戈沙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tyrn Gorthad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.50,0:25:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人類稱爲古冢崗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Known to Men as the Barrow-downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:25:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在遠古時代 這裏是他們的領主和國王安息的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In ancient days, this was where they laid their lords and kings to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.66,0:26:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏沒有安息的氣息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel no rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.12,0:26:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就連樹木也顯得不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the trees seem ill at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.66,0:26:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不用怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fear not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.58,0:26:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,死人構不成威脅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dead Men are no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.33,0:26:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.20,0:26:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,四體僵冷 刺骨入心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cold be hand and heart and bone
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.04,0:26:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,巖洞長眠寒似冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And cold be sleep under stone
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.75,0:26:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有一瞬間 我好像聽到...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a moment, I thought I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.70,0:26:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.87,0:26:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽到什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.62,0:27:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來像是一首歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was almost like a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.00,0:27:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,或是一首歌的回憶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the memory of a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.04,0:27:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.25,0:27:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這些護甲出自林頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their barding is from Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.83,0:27:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,至高王派了人去警告凱勒布林博\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The King sent a dispatch to warn Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.16,0:27:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是這人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This dispatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.91,0:27:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要趕快離開這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must go from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.45,0:27:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,–戴莫爾  –抓住我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Daemor! - Hold on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.75,0:27:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,別放手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.08,0:28:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,四體僵冷 刺骨入心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cold old be hand and heart and bone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.58,0:28:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,巖洞長眠寒似冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And cold be sleep under stone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.50,0:28:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如今墓穴長眠罷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never more to wake on stony bed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.91,0:28:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,直到日月隕落不再明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never, till the Sun fails and the Moon is dead
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.12,0:28:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,黑風吹襲 星辰將晦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the black wind the stars shall die
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.54,0:28:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,準備迎戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prepare yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.58,0:28:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是什麼東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.45,0:28:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,古冢屍妖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barrow-wights.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.70,0:29:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,攻擊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.66,0:29:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,箭不虛發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still your arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.20,0:29:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的武器對他們沒用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're impervious to our weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.62,0:29:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,撐住 跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold fast. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.45,0:29:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.75,0:29:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,–幫我打開 –什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Help me open it. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.83,0:29:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.87,0:29:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,第二指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.12,0:30:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.62,0:30:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.45,0:30:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,根據傳說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to lore,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只有埋葬他們的刀劍 才能讓他們安息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}only the blades with which they were buried will return such creatures to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.00,0:30:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但這些人已經埋葬千年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the Men buried here have been entombed for over a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.45,0:30:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看來有東西喚醒了他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it is safe to say that something has awoken them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.95,0:30:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.08,0:30:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.62,0:30:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喚醒了邪惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Awakening evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.33,0:30:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,整個中洲的邪惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Across all of Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.70,0:30:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo! Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.66,0:30:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,–西奧  –西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Theo! Theo! Theo! Theo! Theo! - Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.00,0:31:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.08,0:31:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.04,0:31:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,–西奧  –西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Theo! -Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.00,0:31:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把武器都留了下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They left all their weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.37,0:31:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對野人來說 斧頭比金子還值錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To a Wildman, an axe-head is worth more than gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.04,0:31:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒把武器帶走太奇怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strange, they did not take it with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.79,0:31:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大家過來 我們繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come, all of you. We move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.62,0:31:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊 來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.41,0:31:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要折磨自己 努曼諾爾人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not torture yourself, Númenórean.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.62,0:31:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧經歷過更糟的情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo has survived far worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.08,0:31:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他會活下來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He will weather this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.37,0:31:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.75,0:31:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.41,0:32:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.70,0:32:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的 往這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You there. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.12,0:32:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,突襲他們營地吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say we raid their camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.29,0:32:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會挑起戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd be starting a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.00,0:32:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,已經開戰了 臭海人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're already at war, Sea-folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.12,0:32:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我所看到的 我不認爲是凡人做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I saw, I do not believe was done by mortal Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.37,0:32:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不是人 是野獸 有必要還會吃人肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not Men. They're animals. They'd eat human flesh if they had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.45,0:33:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我們每浪費一分鐘 西奧就多一分危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every minute we waste is another Theo's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.37,0:33:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要繼續找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got to keep searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.66,0:33:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以去伊斯菲爾谷看看 聽說野人在那裏紮營\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could canvass Eastfield Glen. Whispers are, Wildmen camp there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.91,0:33:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.00,0:33:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,最好往北看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd do better to look north.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.20,0:33:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why north?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.45,0:33:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了好幾個星期 在這片大地尋找我愛的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've spent weeks searching these lands, lookin' for loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.08,0:33:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,北方那片森林很古老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That part of the forest is old.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.00,0:33:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏肯定有野人 甚至更可怕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise you, there are Wildmen there, and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.70,0:33:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,阿隆迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arondir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.25,0:33:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,別浪費大白天了 收集飲水和糧食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's not waste any daylight. Gather water and provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.62,0:33:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.37,0:33:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.54,0:33:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你漏了一個地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You missed a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.83,0:34:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.75,0:34:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你們島上應該從來不缺水吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fancy you never want for water on your island.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.16,0:34:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 努曼諾爾家家戶戶都有水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. In Númenor, we have water in most of our homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.41,0:34:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真想看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.54,0:34:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你未婚夫肯定也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wager your betrothed would too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.66,0:34:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,該繼續前進了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We ought to keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.20,0:34:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.41,0:34:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲翠 你說你跟野人相處過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You say you spent time among the Wildmen, Estrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.45,0:34:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.62,0:34:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒跟他們相處 我躲起來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, I wasn't exactly among them. I was hidin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.54,0:34:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,–他們有傷害你嗎  –阿隆迪爾 你幹嘛...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did they ever do you harm? - Arondir, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.83,0:34:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我問是因爲我發現你脖子上有傷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ask because I noticed a wound on your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.29,0:34:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來是最近弄傷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks to be recent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.62,0:34:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我自己弄的 我在火邊睡着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. That was my fault. I, um... fell asleep by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.83,0:34:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該熄滅的 但那晚太冷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should've put it out, but the night was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.91,0:34:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是我太蠢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was foolish of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.08,0:34:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們難免都會做蠢事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all do foolish things sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.95,0:34:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是在絕望的時刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially in moments of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.45,0:35:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲翠 那是什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.29,0:35:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,自己燒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Self-burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.91,0:35:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,野人以此隱藏阿達爾印記\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Wildmen do it to hide the Mark of Adar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是她跟你進來 在入口處就會逮到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We would have caught her at the gate had she not come in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.20,0:35:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說她是野人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a Wildman?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.12,0:35:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她是他們的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.25,0:35:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她會帶我們找到其他野人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she's going to lead us to all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.08,0:35:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你本來打算怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.45,0:35:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,攻擊我 搶走我的馬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stab me? Take my horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.91,0:35:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was that it? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.45,0:35:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,後來你發現我是努曼諾爾人 想到更好的主意 對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you saw I was a Númenórean. Had a better idea, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.75,0:35:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在利用我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were using me all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.95,0:35:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本沒未婚夫吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wager you don't even have a betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.58,0:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,–你寧願我死在魔多  –不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Would you rather I died in Mordor? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.91,0:36:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.41,0:36:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,別動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be still.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.75,0:36:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.41,0:36:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧根本不是被人類抓走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo was not taken by Men at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.70,0:37:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.54,0:37:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小胖醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well-fed's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.37,0:37:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.87,0:37:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,外面那是什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.41,0:37:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 不管是什麼 一定很大隻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't know yet. But whatever they are, they're big.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.16,0:37:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小心腳下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.95,0:37:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,能用手的話會比較好平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might be easier to balance if I had use of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.95,0:38:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也比較好逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And easier to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.95,0:38:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣沒人逃得掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one could escape in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.29,0:38:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我解開吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, unlock me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.54,0:38:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,別動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be still.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.08,0:38:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我說我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.87,0:38:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,手給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.87,0:38:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.54,0:38:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拉我起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lift me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.91,0:38:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要沉下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,剛那是什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.54,0:39:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,世界深處多的是無名之物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are nameless things in the deep places of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.58,0:40:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這一個...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.25,0:40:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們稱之爲“晚餐”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we shall call "supper."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.75,0:40:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我跟村裏的長老商量過了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, I've conferred with the village elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.75,0:40:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,日出時把你們兩個趕出去 抱歉 但壯軀族優先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two are to be cast out at sunrise. Sorry, but Stoors must come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.87,0:40:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說 換作是他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Truth is, he was in your place...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.45,0:40:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,換作是薩道克也會這麼做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc likely would've done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.29,0:40:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,薩道克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.66,0:40:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的尋路人 他叫薩道克布羅斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our trail-finder. He was called Sadoc Burrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.54,0:40:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你們領袖叫薩道克布羅斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc Burrows was your leader's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.87,0:40:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信你 只是想確認一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just so's we're both working with a full bushel, I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.66,0:40:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你看這個只是想充分確認\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm only showin' you this to make good and sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.66,0:40:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,確認什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.12,0:41:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,相傳在古代有個壯軀族人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Story goes, in ancient days, there was a Stoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.70,0:41:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我們其他人很不一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wasn't like the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.79,0:41:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,據說有天晚上他夢到一個地方 那裏有一望無際的清涼溪流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They say he dreamed one night of a place, with endless streams of cold water
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.83,0:41:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,綿延起伏的柔軟山丘 不用一個月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and rollin' hills so soft, a family could dig a hole
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.50,0:41:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一家人就能挖個洞住進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and live in it in less than a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.91,0:41:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他稱那裏爲“蘇薩”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He called it "the S?zat."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.62,0:41:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有一年他帶着一羣追隨者出發尋找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Struck out one year with a caravan of followers to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.70,0:41:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,承諾等他找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promised, when he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.33,0:41:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,會派人回來帶我們大家過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he'd send someone back to gather the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.45,0:41:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我們最後一次聽到 羅裏馬斯布羅斯這名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that was the last any of us ever heard of Rorimas Burrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.79,0:41:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,波比的行腳之歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poppy's walkin' song.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.79,0:41:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,毛腳族來過這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harfoots have been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.83,0:42:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你的村子 你的家鄉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your kind's home, where you come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.29,0:42:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來像這樣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}does it look like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.54,0:42:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是回來帶我們大家去蘇薩的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you come back here to lead us all to the S?zat?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.00,0:42:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.50,0:42:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,羅裏馬斯從未找到蘇薩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rorimas never found the S?zat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.12,0:42:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,過了好久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And after a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.66,0:42:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直在流浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we just kept wanderin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.20,0:42:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒有家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.29,0:42:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,騎馬人來了 大傢伙 這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The riders sighted. Big folk. Comin' this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.79,0:43:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,各位大駕光臨...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To what do we owe the pleasure of--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.41,0:43:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,毛腳族人 在哪裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Harfoots, where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.16,0:43:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這片沙漠我們唯一知道的半身人 就只有壯軀族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only halflings we know about in this desert are Stoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.58,0:43:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我們爲何戴面具嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know why we wear these masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.45,0:44:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,敢反抗黑巫師 等他親自過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Defy the Dark Wizard and, when we return with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.50,0:44:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就會知道答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will find out for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.08,0:44:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你認爲這戒指在欺騙我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you believe this Ring is deceiving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.58,0:44:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我相信它在指引我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I believe it is guiding me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.12,0:44:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,跟隨指引可能是我們 通往勝利的唯一道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that following it may be our only path to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.00,0:44:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一勝利的代價變得太大呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there no point at which the cost of victory becomes too great?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.04,0:44:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒到那個地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have yet to reach that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.45,0:44:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼就不害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How does that not terrify you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.04,0:44:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲索隆統治世界所帶來的苦難\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because the suffering of a world ruled by Sauron
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.87,0:45:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,更讓我害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}terrifies me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.70,0:45:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都能感覺到 但戴上戒指後 我能清楚看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have always felt it. But with this Ring, I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.45,0:45:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果無法完成眼前的任務 我們將失去一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything we stand to lose if we fail in the task before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.66,0:45:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親預見了 有一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father foresaw that, one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.41,0:45:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,凱勒布林博的命運會掌握在我手裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor's life would be in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.83,0:45:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我會選擇我該走的路 拚盡全力加以保護\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will choose the path I must to give me the best hope of protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.87,0:45:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,保護最脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Protecting that which is most fragile,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,最珍貴的東西是所有精靈的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}most dear, is a task entrusted to all Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.75,0:45:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這個使命尚未完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And one that is not yet complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.20,0:46:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對還會有更多痛苦的犧牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I promise you, there will be more painful sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.70,0:46:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.50,0:46:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,答應我 埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise me, Elrond,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.95,0:46:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你會把消滅索隆放在第一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will put opposing Sauron above all other considerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.75,0:46:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至優先於我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.95,0:46:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會答應被戒指左右之人任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will make no promise whose asking is borne of that Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.70,0:46:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但我發誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I swear to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.37,0:46:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,消滅索隆會是第一要務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}defeating Sauron will come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.33,0:46:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至優先於你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.58,0:46:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,指揮官 抱歉打擾 我們聽到鼓聲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, commander, we heard drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.66,0:47:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是手銬的鑰匙嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that the key to the manacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.62,0:47:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他是要讓你決定用不用吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Believe he meant for you to decide whether or not to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.87,0:47:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.12,0:48:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.08,0:48:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 伊熙爾杜 那個...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Isildur, y'see...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.66,0:48:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,像我這種人不會得到原諒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgiveness doesn't come to folk like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.75,0:48:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他們遲早會趕我走 你很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sooner or later, they'll cast me out, you know they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.33,0:48:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓他們這麼做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.25,0:48:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓他們趕你走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't let them cast you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.62,0:48:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,放下劍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put down the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.79,0:48:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲翠 放下劍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid, drop the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.25,0:48:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲翠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.16,0:49:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.08,0:49:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大綠林的阿隆迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am Arondir, of the Greenwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.04,0:49:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾拿斧頭砍過樹木嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hast thou ever touched axe to wooded life?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.33,0:49:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很痛苦 但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To my great pain, I have, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.33,0:49:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.20,0:49:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是爲了砍下樹木\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is not for felling trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.20,0:50:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是爲了什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does it fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.62,0:50:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,奧克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.66,0:50:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,退後\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.16,0:50:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有一支...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was an...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.16,0:50:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,奧克大軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}an army of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.91,0:50:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊行進 一邊屠殺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maiming and murdering as they marched.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.12,0:50:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們看到他們乾的好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We saw what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.62,0:50:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你們纔來這 才這麼生氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that why you're here? Why you're so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.29,0:50:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,噴濺的樹液和燃燒的樹枝 從遠處呼喚我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The spilling sap and burning branch called to us from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.83,0:50:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...我們來得太遲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But... we were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.58,0:50:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大軍 多久以前的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An army? How long ago was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.66,0:50:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,冬花從這些樹還小就滋養他們長大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winterbloom nourished many of those trees from seed and sprout.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.87,0:50:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,別要她再多說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not ask her to speak more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.83,0:50:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他們跟他們沒兩樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are no different from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.33,0:51:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,連根拔起 砍斷樹枝 劈開樹幹 壞事做盡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disemboweling, and uprooting, branch-breakers and trunk-splitters, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.41,0:51:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們應當\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We would seek...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.00,0:51:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爲造成的傷害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your forgiveness...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.04,0:51:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,誠摯懇求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.50,0:51:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的原諒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...we have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.54,0:51:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒需要時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgiveness takes an age.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.16,0:52:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要等雨水洗去土壤的沉痛記憶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rain washing clear the long memory of soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.29,0:52:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,新鮮樹皮覆蓋陳舊傷疤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New bark, covering old scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在這段時間裏 我保證\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in all that time, I promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.45,0:52:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會確保這片森林平靜祥和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will see to it that the trees of this wood are left in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.20,0:52:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他們知道什麼意思嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think they know what peace is?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.08,0:52:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚暴風雨過後\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is what comes after the night storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.00,0:52:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明寧靜 鳥兒甦醒那個片刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the dawn is silent, and the birds awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.70,0:52:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在山脈拔地而起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have tended this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.20,0:52:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,切割大地之前 我們就在照料這片森林了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since before the mountains rose up and divided it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.79,0:53:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那時這裏唯一的聲音 只有苔蘚沐浴陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the only sound here was the light upon the moss...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.25,0:53:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.33,0:53:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和樹葉呼吸起伏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the breathing of the leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.58,0:53:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我們知道平靜祥和什麼意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. We know peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.50,0:53:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲翠 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.87,0:53:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲翠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid? Estrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.25,0:53:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哈根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hagen?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.50,0:53:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,–我以爲... –我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What... I thought you... - So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.75,0:53:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信真的是你 看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe you're here. Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.62,0:54:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你來救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for coming for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.62,0:54:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了承諾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.70,0:54:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你信守承諾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for keepin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.70,0:54:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我要信守另一個承諾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I must keep another.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.87,0:54:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,奧克不斷前進 我要跟上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Orcs are on the move. I must follow the trail where it leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.62,0:54:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定有機會再次對上阿達爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps have another chance to confront Adar.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.70,0:54:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要的話你可以跟我一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can come with me, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.83,0:54:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我有自己的承諾要信守\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have promises of my own to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.37,0:55:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那再見了 佩拉基爾領主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then mae glenno. Lord of Pelargir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.12,0:55:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,南方
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.04,0:55:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,埃瑞吉安
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.37,0:55:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,奧克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Orc-treachery.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.91,0:55:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那條路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.79,0:55:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看來是通往...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gather it leads to--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.04,0:55:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,埃瑞吉安 大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eregion, my liege.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.04,0:56:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來找索隆 卻找到阿達爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We came in search of Sauron. And instead, we find Adar?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.83,0:56:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是一夥的還是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could they be in league with each other or...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.70,0:56:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在戰鬥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.91,0:56:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,奧克大軍進軍精靈王國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A legion of Orcs have marched into Elvish lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.37,0:56:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我們所有人都在戰鬥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are all of us at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.87,0:56:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在我們的大軍前往魔多之前 要讓至高王知道這消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Word of this must reach the High King before our host sails for Mordor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.37,0:56:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.41,0:56:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.37,0:56:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的晚餐跑掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's our supper gettin' away!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.50,0:56:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.95,0:56:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,歸隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.20,0:56:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰 繼續找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is it? Keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.66,0:56:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就在附近 繼續找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're nearby. Keep lookin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.70,0:57:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰 那什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is it? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.08,0:57:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊傳來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Came from over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.37,0:57:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我聞到精靈的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can smell an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.45,0:57:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太神奇了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.41,0:57:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,給我徹底找 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave no stone unturned. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.75,0:57:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,快去林頓 我會盡力拖延他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get to Lindon. I will occupy them as long as I am able.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.37,0:57:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.20,0:57:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.08,0:57:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,埃爾隆德 拿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it, Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.16,0:58:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.50,0:58:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.95,0:58:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stand alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.37,0:58:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,砍下她的右手拇指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut off her right thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.95,0:58:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快說其他的在哪 就留你左手拇指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell us where the others are, I'll let you keep the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.29,0:59:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她犧牲自己拯救我們大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She sacrificed herself to save us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.04,0:59:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你錯了 坎尼爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you are mistaken, Camnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.70,0:59:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她這麼做不是爲了救我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She did not do it to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.20,0:59:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.45,0:59:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是爲了救戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She did it to save the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.87,0:59:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.58,0:59:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏是精靈領地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These are Elven lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.37,0:59:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,滾回魔影去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go back to the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.33,1:00:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一顆星照耀着我們相遇的時刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A star shines on the hour of our meeting...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.58,1:00:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,加拉德瑞爾夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.08,1:00:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,歌聲起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let the song begin
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.79,1:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us sing together
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.16,1:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,歌唱那太陽 星星 月亮與輕霧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of sun, stars, moon and mist,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.16,1:00:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,雨水與雲天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rain and cloudy weather
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.87,1:00:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,唱那新芽上的陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Light on the budding leaf
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.58,1:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,羽毛上的露珠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dew on the feather
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.25,1:00:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,開曠山頭的風\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wind on the open hill
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.95,1:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,帚石南的花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bells on the heather
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.70,1:00:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,身條細如柳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O slender as a willow-wand
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.04,1:00:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,心地比水清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O clearer than clear water
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.12,1:00:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,清流照蘆葦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O reed by the living pool
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.75,1:00:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,美麗的河之女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fair River-daughter
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.50,1:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,春日復夏日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O springtime and summertime
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.79,1:01:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,來年春又臨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And spring again after
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.04,1:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,風吹流泉上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O wind on the waterfall
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.50,1:01:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,笑動萬夜鳴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the leaves' laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.20,1:01:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老湯姆邦巴迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Tom Bombadil
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.95,1:01:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,樂天老夥計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is a merry fellow
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.58,1:01:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他身穿外套天藍色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bright blue his jacket is
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.25,1:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,腳蹬黃皮靴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And his boots are yellow
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.95,1:01:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,唱那幽池的蘆葦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reeds by the shady pool
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.66,1:01:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,水中的睡蓮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lilies on the water
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.33,1:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就像老湯姆邦巴迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Tom Bombadil
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.04,1:01:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,與河流的女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the River-daughter
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.79,1:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,身條細如柳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O slender as a willow-wand
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.08,1:01:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,心地比水清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O clearer than clear water
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.25,1:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,清流照蘆葦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O reed by the living pool
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.79,1:01:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,美麗的河之女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fair River-daughter
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.66,1:01:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,春日復夏日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O springtime and summertime
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.79,1:02:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,來年春又臨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And spring again after
